CIMA Labs in deal with Bristol - Myers . CIMA Labs Inc said Thursday it introduced its OraSolv dosage form of Bristol - Myers Squibb Co ' s children ' s Tempra products in the United States . Introductory quantities of the product were manufactured at CIMA ' s Eden Prairie , Minnesota facility . OraSolv incorporates drugs into tablets that dissolve quickly in the mouth . CIMA is a drug delivery company that develops and manufactures products based upon its OraSolv technology for marketing by multinational pharmaceutical companies . ( ( - - Chicago newsdesk , 312 - 408 - 8787 ) ) 
